    	<div class="comment_content">
    		<p>Thank you for the comments.  I really love the &#8220;life of quality&#8221; and will do my part to make that more of the vernacular.</p>
<p>CMS has not raised this more because of the political hot button issue that it is.  This issue needs to be raised by all of us so CMS doesn&#8217;t have to do it.  Great groups are out there working on it &#8211; National Healthcare Decision Day, Engage With Grace, Five Wishes, and many others are working hard to change the conversation.  I&#8217;m grateful they are out there and feel the tide will continue to turn.</p>

    	</div>

		
